channel.title: Noob question
channel.description:
This is a really noob question lol..
I made a new home. When i log in with a new account im at my new home right.
When i click, in the mage book, 'home' how do i make it to take me to my new home? not the old one?
And its got different sets, when i click home it goes to 1 of like 5 different squares, all in the same area, just different squares.
Thanks
